memberdef.name: profiler_start
memberdef.initializer: do \ { \ MHO_Profiler::GetInstance().Lock(); \ MHO_Profiler::GetInstance().AddEntry(pStart, std::hash< std::thread::id >{}(std::this_thread::get_id()), \ std::string(sn::file_basename(__FILE__)), __LINE__, \ std::string(__PRETTY_FUNCTION__)); \ MHO_Profiler::GetInstance().Unlock(); \ } \ while(0)
